                            <comment id="13691468" author="steffkes" created="Sun, 23 Jun 2013 14:14:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Having a long history, with problems in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3238&quot; title=&quot;Sequel of Admin UI&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-3238&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-3238&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4176&quot; title=&quot;analysis ui: javascript not properly handling URL decoding of input&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-4176&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-4176&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, hopefully it now does the job it&apos;s supposed to do *g&lt;/p&gt;

